@page "/about"

<PageTitle>About</PageTitle>

<div class="about-page page-blur-container">
    <h1>About LogiHUB</h1>

    <p>
        LogiHUB is a centralized logistics and shipment management platform designed to streamline
        operations for businesses of all sizes. Our goal is to provide an intuitive interface
        to track shipments, manage customers, automate invoicing, and monitor delivery status
        in real-time.
    </p>

    <p>
        With LogiHUB, companies can reduce manual processes, improve accuracy, and gain valuable
        insights into their logistics workflows. Whether you're handling a few shipments a day or
        managing thousands, LogiHUB is built to scale with your business.
    </p>

    <p>
        The platform emphasizes ease-of-use, speed, and transparency, making it the ideal solution
        for businesses looking to optimize their shipping and customer management operations.
    </p>
</div>